*nfs-utils-1.0.7-r2 (08 Oct 2005)

  08 Oct 2005; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org>
  +files/nfs-utils-1.0.7-man-pages.patch, files/nfs, files/nfs.confd,
  +nfs-utils-1.0.7-r2.ebuild:
