  Corrected init script to use 'svc_stop; svc_start' and not 'stop; start'.

  15 Mar 2005; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  nfs-utils-1.0.7-r1.ebuild:
  add kerberos to IUSE

